},
["text"] = "|Hplayer:Gnomegoat-Ragnaros:495:SAY:|h[|cffaad372Gnomegoat|r]|h says: feqeqqeq",
["id"] = "s0_103",
["timestamp"] = 1783888023,
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
["g"] = 1,
["r"] = 1,
},
["text"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal says: Your house is starting to look like a home. The items you remove will still be available in your house chest if you change your mind.",
["id"] = "s0_104",
["timestamp"] = 1783888188,
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
["g"] = 1,
["r"] = 1,
},
["text"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal says: The house is looking much more orderly. You're fortunate none of that clutter was load-bearing.",
["id"] = "s0_105",
["timestamp"] = 1783888201,
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
["g"] = 1,
["r"] = 1,
},
["text"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal says: It's time to decorate! I look forward to seeing what you do with the place.",
["id"] = "s0_106",
["timestamp"] = 1783888690,
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
["g"] = 1,
["r"] = 1,
},
["text"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal says: Your house chest is brimming with possibilities. Pull out whatever sparks joy and give it the perfect spot.",
["id"] = "s0_107",
["timestamp"] = 1783888696,
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
["g"] = 1,
["r"] = 1,
},
["text"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal says: The floors, walls, and ceiling are your palette. Place what you want, where you want it.",
["id"] = "s0_108",
["timestamp"] = 1783888719,
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
["g"] = 1,
["r"] = 1,
},
["text"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal says: It looks like you've got the hang of decorating. I can't wait to see what more you can do, given time.",
["id"] = "s0_109",
["timestamp"] = 1783888736,
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
["g"] = 1,
["r"] = 1,
},
["text"] = "Lyssabel Dawnpetal says: There are a number of vendors in the town center who sell decor for your home. You should stop by and introduce yourself.",
["id"] = "s0_110",
["timestamp"] = 1783888762,
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Local",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
["g"] = 1,
["r"] = 1,
},
["text"] = "Local says: Heard you purchased a new home. Hope you enjoy it!",
["id"] = "s0_111",
["timestamp"] = 1783888793,
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Local",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
["g"] = 1,
["r"] = 1,
},
["text"] = "Local says: Ooh, cheese! Is it aged?",
["id"] = "s0_112",
["timestamp"] = 1783888811,
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Blood Elf Guest",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
["g"] = 1,
["r"] = 1,
},
["text"] = "Blood Elf Guest says: This is one of our younger varieties. Only about twelve hundred years.",
["id"] = "s0_113",
["timestamp"] = 1783888812,
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Local",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
["g"] = 1,
["r"] = 1,
},
["text"] = "Local says: That's a good age.",
["id"] = "s0_114",
["timestamp"] = 1783888816,
},
