["timestamp"] = 1783974427,
["id"] = "s0_529",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["class"] = "HUNTER",
["race"] = "Gnome",
["name"] = "Gnomegoat",
["sex"] = 2,
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_LOOT",
["type"] = "LOOT",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 0,
["g"] = 0.6666666865348816,
["b"] = 0,
},
["text"] = "You receive loot: |cnIQ0:|Hitem:260670::::::::80:255:::::::::|h[Bloody Broken Beak]|h|r",
["timestamp"] = 1783974427,
["id"] = "s0_530",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Arator",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 1,
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
},
["text"] = "Arator says: The Lightbloom first appeared when the Sunwell was restored, many years ago. But it never grew near civilization like this.",
["timestamp"] = 1783974453,
["id"] = "s0_531",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["class"] = "HUNTER",
["race"] = "Gnome",
["name"] = "Gnomegoat",
["sex"] = 2,
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_EMOTE",
["type"] = "MONSTER_EMOTE",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 0.501960813999176,
["b"] = 0.250980406999588,
},
["text"] = "You sense a nearby Skyriding Glyph.",
["timestamp"] = 1783974461,
["id"] = "s0_532",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Arator",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 1,
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
},
["text"] = "Arator says: Perhaps this sudden growth is tied to the empowerment of the Sunwell. I think I was right--this could be used to help the Vanguard.",
["timestamp"] = 1783974475,
["id"] = "s0_533",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Arator",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 1,
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
},
["text"] = "Arator says: That creature must have come from the Lightbloom! We should let the Magistrix know.",
["timestamp"] = 1783974498,
["id"] = "s0_534",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Arator",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 1,
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
},
["text"] = "Arator says: What happened here?",
["timestamp"] = 1783974515,
["id"] = "s0_535",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Melida Sunward",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 1,
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
},
["text"] = "Melida Sunward says: Hawkstriders... running amok...",
["timestamp"] = 1783974516,
["id"] = "s0_536",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Melida Sunward",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 1,
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
},
["text"] = "Melida Sunward says: Thank you. Those hawkstriders are a terror!",
["timestamp"] = 1783974528,
["id"] = "s0_537",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["class"] = "HUNTER",
["race"] = "Gnome",
["name"] = "Gnomegoat",
["sex"] = 2,
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_EMOTE",
["type"] = "MONSTER_EMOTE",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 0.501960813999176,
["b"] = 0.250980406999588,
},
["text"] = "You sense a nearby Skyriding Glyph.",
["timestamp"] = 1783974530,
["id"] = "s0_538",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Arator",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 1,
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
},
["text"] = "Arator says: They shouldn't be a problem much longer.",
["timestamp"] = 1783974531,
["id"] = "s0_539",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Arator",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 1,
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
},
["text"] = "Arator says: The nearest Lightbloom is nowhere near the village. How did the growth get all the way out here?",
["timestamp"] = 1783974544,
["id"] = "s0_540",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Orweyna",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 1,
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
},
["text"] = "Orweyna says: This Lightbloom you describe is clearly out of control. We must find what has disturbed it so.",
["timestamp"] = 1783974556,
["id"] = "s0_541",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["class"] = "HUNTER",
["race"] = "Gnome",
["name"] = "Gnomegoat",
["sex"] = 2,
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_LOOT",
["type"] = "LOOT",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 0,
["g"] = 0.6666666865348816,
["b"] = 0,
},
["text"] = "You receive item: |cnIQ2:|Hitem:248026::::::::80:255::11:2:13573:6652:2:9:80:28:3085:::::|h[Lynxslayer's Scale Grips]|h|r",
["timestamp"] = 1783974564,
["id"] = "s0_542",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Lyssara Duskmourne",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 1,
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
},
["text"] = "Lyssara Duskmourne says: The shadows hang long with the crimes of the meek...",
["timestamp"] = 1783974569,
["id"] = "s0_543",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["name"] = "Lyssara Duskmourne",
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_SAY",
["type"] = "MONSTER_SAY",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 1,
["g"] = 1,
["b"] = 0.6235294342041016,
},
["text"] = "Lyssara Duskmourne says: Go seek out which company has soiled these shores. Meet me back here once you are done.",
["timestamp"] = 1783974572,
["id"] = "s0_544",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
["player"] = {
["class"] = "HUNTER",
["race"] = "Gnome",
["name"] = "Gnomegoat",
["sex"] = 2,
},
["event"] = "CHAT_MSG_LOOT",
["type"] = "LOOT",
},
["color"] = {
["r"] = 0,
["g"] = 0.6666666865348816,
["b"] = 0,
},
["text"] = "You receive loot: |cnIQ0:|Hitem:260670::::::::80:255:::::::::|h[Bloody Broken Beak]|h|r",
["timestamp"] = 1783974602,
["id"] = "s0_545",
},
{
["recordedBy"] = "Gnomegoat-Ragnaros",
["typeInfo"] = {
